[49m[38;5;10m+     1[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Recipe 11.9: Care Coordination Assistant
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     2[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     3[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Complexity:** Complex · **Phase:** Regulated · **Estimated Cost:** ~$3-12 per active member per month (depends on engagement frequency, channel mix, model choice, RAG depth, EHR-integration depth, referral-network-integration depth, and human-care-manager-escalation overhead)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     4[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
